UseSolrWithUquery
=================

This plugin allow you to display the results from Solr using the
javascript uQuery library.

Installation
============

1. Add routes :

map.solr

2. Rake task to copy files from the plugin into your application

  $ rake use_solr_with_uquery:install
  - copy jquery / UI files into public folder
  - create configuration file and config loader

